HEADWORD: betatron
<hw>be"ta*tron</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a type of particle accelerator
which accelerates a continuous beam of electrons to high speeds by means
of the electric field produced by changing magnetic flux.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> induction accelerator.</syn>⟦br⟧
